name: en-map_admin
title: Install IIAB Maps
description:
Download an IIAB Map Pack for your continent, and Hi-Res Satellite Photos for your local region(s) using the

Admin Console Install Content -> Get Map Regions
extra_description:
You can remove this stub from your IIAB home page using Admin Console Content Menus -> Content Item List.

See also the full instructions for IIAB Maps.
